# This OpenMP exercise directory contains
#  01/        - your working directory including skeletons for all exercises
#  solution/  - here you find solutions for all exercises
#  tasks/     - this is a copy of 01/ for example to be able to
#               compare your result with the originally provided skeleton
#  README
#  README.html Same as README, but with html header
#
# For the case, you want to allow several participants working of the same file-store
# you may use several working directories 00, 01, 02, 03, ...
# In each of the user working directories 00, 01, 02,  
# one must copy the content of tasks/ into those working directories, e.g. with
# 
#      cp -rp tasks 02 
#      ... 
#
# (It is already done for directory 01, but not for any other user directories.)
